Puppet module: gems

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages gems software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include gems              # Install and run gems with standard configurations.
include gems::disable     # Disable gems service.
include gems::disableboot # Disable gems service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include gems::absent      # Remove gems package.

DEPENDENCIES:
